$ON_RFGNBR
Onevent CONTROL Call C_RFGNBR(zc) From W1HRMAT4
Return

Subprog C_RFGNBR(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
## Action STD
Call C_RFGNBR(VALEUR) From SUBEML2
If mkstat : GERR = 1 : GZONE = "RFGNBR" : GZNUM = 1120 : Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

$CHG_STY
Return


